What is geist?
==============

Geist is nothing.


What Does Geist Require?
========================

Geist needs libxml2, imlib2 (RECENT CVS)


What will geist be?
===================

Geist will be an object-based image creation/layout application.

Think visio/illustrator with some of the good bits of *gasp* powerpoint.

But cooler.

And let's not forget the extra added giblet special ingredient.
